examples.text: Mr. <w>Newberry</w> has been teaching history at the local college for over twenty years.
We invited the entire <w>Newberry</w> family to the wedding reception next month.

senses.sense_definition: A place name used for several cities and towns in the United States, particularly in South Carolina, Michigan, and Florida.

examples.text: They decided to stop in <w>Newberry</w> for lunch while driving through the state.
The historic opera house is one of the main attractions in downtown <w>Newberry</w>.
